metadata.name: The Curve
metadata.description:
I present you the 2nd version of Tranquillity.

Tranquillity is a collection targeting the calmness that is missing from our everyday life.

In an ever changing world, we so often don't have the time to take a step back and reflect.

In this collection, there will be a continuation of previously loved NFTs and also a deeper look to my feelings and thoughts with the help of AI.
